# f9b5f7c71b7342e780989bc88bb16e0b
#: ../../developer-guide/architecture/api-functions.en.rst:62
msgid ""
"A preprocessor macro which computes the maximum size of a fragment based "
"on the value of :arg:`big`. This is computed as if the argument where the"
" value of the :arg:`big` field in a struct :cpp:class:`Dir`."
msgstr ""

# 1c0cb691668d455bb2c1fe9b605ba7a7
#: ../../developer-guide/architecture/api-functions.en.rst:68
msgid ""
"A preprocessor macro which computes the block size multiplier for a "
"struct :cpp:class:`Dir` where :arg:`big` is the :arg:`big` field value."
msgstr ""

